nodes.text:
Gerald Home (born October 18, 1950) is the mime artist/actor of Tessek the Quarren and a Mon Calamari officer Verrack in Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi.
Since January 2008, he has acted as the official ambassador of S.W.O.R.A., the Star Wars Outer Rim Alliance.
